{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_09_03",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 3話 気付いたら大きくなっていた",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――新曲のジャケット撮影日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of new song's cover shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん、もうすぐ本番ですが\n準備の方は――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san‚ we're about to start shooting‚\nare you ready――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 6.3333333254
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ………………チラ、チラ\nはぁ～～～～～～…………チラチラ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa……………… Glance‚ glance\nHaa～～～～～～………… Glancing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5885170847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 15.8340135972
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "…………あの、遙子さん？\nどうかしましたか、これ見よがしに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…………Um‚ Haruko-san?\nIs something wrong? You're being so obvious",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.3006802718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 21.5340135972
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "べ、別にこれ見よがしじゃないもん\nただね、さっきもスタッフさん達に気を遣われちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-It's not like I'm being obvious or anything.\nIt's just that the staff were being considerate of me again‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 31.224240454
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "もう、最近どこに行ってもそうなのよ！\n同じ時期にデビューした子に挨拶したら敬語で返されて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and that's been happening everywhere I go lately!\nWhen I greeted someone who debuted at the same time as me‚ they replied formally‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "馴染みの局のスタッフさんが、重そうに荷物を\n運んでたから手伝おうとしたら、慌てて断られ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and when a familiar TV station staff member\nwas carrying something heavy‚ I tried to help but they refused in a panic…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 46.8726303975
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "も～！　なんでそんなに気を遣うのよ～！\n昔はこんなことなかったのに～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh! Why are they being so considerate!\nThis never happened before~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 54.0001135905
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（は、遙子さん、相当気にしてるみたいだな）\n（まぁ、それだけ続けば仕方ないか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Wow‚ Haruko-san seems really bothered by this.）\n（Well‚ I guess it's understandable if it keeps happening.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.9334469318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 62.1334469239
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あの、そのことについて俺なりに考えてみたんですけど\nやっぱりサニピが\nBIG4になったからじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ I've been thinking about that‚ and\nI think it's because Sunny Peace\nbecame a BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "サニピがBIG4に……？\nだからみんな私に気を遣ってるってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace became BIG4…?\nSo that's why everyone is being considerate of me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 76.5518144209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私はそんなに大御所でもないし\n相変わらず地味だし、クイズ番組でも間違えるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ I'm not a big shot or anything‚\nI'm still plain‚ I make mistakes on quiz shows‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "全然、昔と変わってないわよ？\n肩書が変わったくらいで、そんな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I haven't changed at all from before?\nJust because my title changed‚ that doesn't…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 91.8411769786
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、変わりました。肩書だけじゃなく\nBIG4にふさわしい実力と経験を身に着けました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ you have changed. Not just your title‚ but\nyou've gained the skills and experience worthy of a BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.5078436532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "実力と、経験……\nでも私は、こつこつやってきただけで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Skills and‚ experience…\nBut I've just been working hard…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.6333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 106.5551906028
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "その結果、今があるんですよ\nあ……そろそろ本番ですね。行きましょう、遙子さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And as a result‚ you are where you are now.\nAh… it's almost time. Let's go‚ Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.088523944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 114.6218572694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "（私は、こつこつやってきただけなんだけど……）\n（その結果として、今がある……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I've just been working hard…）\n（And as a result‚ I'm here now…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.2673573571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈ちゃんと、さくらちゃんと、みんなと……）\n（一歩ずつ、一歩ずつ前に進んで……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（With Mana-chan‚ Sakura-chan‚ and everyone…）\n（Taking one step at a time‚ moving forward…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.6333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 128.7341248908
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "（自分でも気付かないくらい）\n（少しずつ、成長していたのかしら……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Without even realizing it）\n（I've grown little by little‚ I wonder…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.1333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "（この撮影みたいに、いつの間にか）\n（周りから大きく見えるくらいに成長して……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Like this shoot‚ before I knew it）\n（I've grown to the point where I look big from the outside…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.6999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 140.1417440173
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "（そっか、{user}君はずっと）\n（それをそばで見ていてくれたから……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（That's right‚ {user} has always been）\n（watching over me from the side…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.3666641235,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4342.631157100015,
          "startTime": 147.7092952806
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.1592950739
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.1592950739
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん、お疲れ様でした\n確認しましたけど、いいジャケットになりそうですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san‚ good work.\nI checked it out‚ and it looks like it'll be a great jacket.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.6759617485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、良かった。ギリギリになっちゃったけど\nこの撮影のコンセプトが、やっと分かったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ I'm glad. It was close‚ but\nI finally understood the concept of this shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.6999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.7099753456
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "怪獣でも、ヒーローでもなくて\nBIG4になった私達を表現していたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not a monster‚ not a hero‚\nit was expressing us who became BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.0999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4に、ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "BIG4?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.5069822547,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.2736489214
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "サニピはデビューしてから、一気に階段を駆け上がって\n気付いたら大きくなっていた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since Sunny Peace debuted‚ we've been climbing the stairs in one go‚\nand before we knew it‚ we had grown so big.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.5666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "等身大のつもりでも\n大きくて、影響力だってある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though we thought we were just being ourselves‚\nwe're big‚ we have influence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.9333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 181.3849187609
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "そのことを忘れないように、っていう\n監督からのメッセージなんだと私は思うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't forget that‚\nthat's what I think the director's message is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.1666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 187.4355992234
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "ご本人に聞いていないから、分からないけれど\n私には、そう伝わってきたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't know because I haven't asked them directly‚ but\nthat's how it came across to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.653680319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、そういう意図が……\nそのコンセプトなら、納得出来たみたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ so that was the intention…\nIt seems like you're convinced with that concept.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.9131727055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、私は気付かない間に、大きく成長していた\nそれを自覚して、時にはふさわしい態度も必要なんだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I had grown big without realizing it.\nI need to be aware of that‚ and sometimes I need to act accordingly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.7333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk022.m4a",
      "text": "気を遣われても、変に嫌がったり慌てないで\nそういうものなんだって、まずは受け入れること",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if they are considerate of me‚ I shouldn't be weirdly annoyed\nor flustered‚ I need to accept that first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 216.8333206176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk023.m4a",
      "text": "それが分からないでわがままを言ってたら\nそれこそ、暴れん坊の怪獣になっちゃうもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I don't understand that and act selfishly‚\nI'll really become a rampaging monster.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.0999852497,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk024.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうね。撮影の前に\n{user}君が言っていた通りだったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. Before the shoot‚\nit was just like {user} said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.4122844896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 232.7533076758
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、遙子さんは成長しています\nマネージャーの俺が保証しますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ Haruko-san‚ you are growing.\nI‚ your manager‚ guarantee it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.0199743425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "大きくなって、もっと周りが見れるようになりましたし\n怜も遙子さんの気遣いに感謝していました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've grown‚ and you can see more of what's around you‚\nand Rei was grateful for your consideration‚ Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.1533076758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 246.2866450702
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk025.m4a",
      "text": "でも、大きくなったからって\n足元はおろそかにしないようにしないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But even though we've grown‚\nwe can't neglect our foundation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.3666631061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 251.5189804627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk026.m4a",
      "text": "もしもの時は、我らがチーフマネージャー君が\n気付かせてくれると思うけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If anything happens‚ I'm sure our chief manager will\nlet us know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 254.7666631061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "チーフマネージャーって……そうですね\n星見プロも俺も、気付いたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chief manager… That's right.\nBoth Hoshimi Pro and I have‚ before we knew it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.2421509577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 265.2754883521
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk027.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、これからも私、沢山悩むと思うけど\n腐ったり後ろを向いたりはしないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ I think I'll be troubled a lot from now on‚\nbut I won't be discouraged or turn back‚ so",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.3333297728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_03-hrk028.m4a",
      "text": "私のこと、ずっとそばで見ていてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "please keep watching over me from the side.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 273.2261684332,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
